## Secrets Management

### Development

```bash
# .env (git-ignored)
DB_USER=dev_user
DB_PASSWORD=dev_password
SERVICE_API_KEY=your-dev-key
```

### Production

```python
# Use a secrets manager
from {{ project_name }}.secrets import get_secret

class ServiceConfig(BaseSettings):
    @property
    def api_key(self) -> str:
        return get_secret("service/api_key")
```

### Never Commit Secrets

```gitignore
# .gitignore
.env
.env.local
*.pem
*_key.json
secrets/
```

