## YAML Config with CLI Overrides

Load base config from YAML, apply `--override key=value` CLI args. Balances reproducibility with flexibility.

**Important**: Nested YAML structure vs flat dataclass fields -- flatten YAML first, THEN apply overrides. Applying overrides to a nested dict loses values.

---

## Profile Inheritance

Use an `inherit_from` field so child profiles only override what they need. Child profiles load the parent, then apply overrides.

