## Environment-Aware Storage

Auto-detect the storage backend based on environment (PostgreSQL in production, SQLite in development, in-memory for tests). Pattern:

```python
def create_storage(env: str = None) -> StorageBackend:
    if env is None:
        env = os.getenv("APP_ENV", "development")
    if env == "production":
        return PostgresStorage(...)
    elif env == "test":
        return InMemoryStorage()
    else:
        return SQLiteStorage(...)
```

